\f1\fs28 P!NG Quick Start Guide\f0\fs22\par
\par

\f1\fs24 Install & Activate\f0\fs22\par
\par
1. \b Install\b0  the plugin by running the .pkg installer. It installs to /Library/Audio/Plug-Ins/ (AU and VST3).\par
2. \b Restart\b0  your DAW (Logic Pro, Ableton, etc.) so it detects P!NG.\par
3. \b Activate\b0  on first use: enter your name and serial number in the activation window, then click Activate.\par
\par
